<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shì gēn jī 迦南563</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì gēn jī, wǒ rén shēng de gēn jī,
 nǐ shì zhù shí, wǒ quán jiā de zhù shí,
 suǒ yǐ wǒ yào tóu kào zài nǐ de yīn xià,
 wǒ hái huó de shí hòu, yào xiàng nǐ gē chàng.</lyrics>
